---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>🧑‍💻 Josh McQueen</h1>
			<p class="tagline">GenAI Strategist &middot; 2x Founder &middot; Builder</p>
			<p>
				I'm a technical AI leader based in San Diego focused on where enterprise strategy meets
				cutting-edge GenAI systems. I've spent 15+ years in cloud platforms and enterprise software,
				including 4+ years building production-grade RAG pipelines, multi-agent workflows, and LLM
				inference solutions.
			</p>
			<p>
				Currently at <strong>AWS</strong> leading enterprise GenAI deployments at scale, and co-founder
				of <strong>FireFlower AI</strong>, a secure GenAI platform for highly regulated industries that
				successfully completed a <a href="https://fireflower.ai/" target="_blank">Phase I SBIR</a> with the United States Air Force. Previously co-founded
				<strong>Arcus Data</strong>, deploying Splunk and big data solutions for large Fortune 100
				companies.
			</p>
			<p>
				I sit at the intersection of deep technical execution and business strategy: helping C-suite
				leaders understand use cases, adoption paths, and real-world impact of AI. Not just the hype.
			</p>

			<h2>What you'll find here</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Thoughts on enterprise AI strategy, GenAI architecture, and model evaluation</li>
				<li>Projects I'm building: vibe-coded apps, experiments, GitHub repos</li>
				<li>Notes on the business of AI: adoption, ROI, and what actually works in production</li>
				<li>Observations from the field working with Fortune 500s, federal agencies, and startups</li>
			</ul>

			<p>
				<a href="/blog">Browse the blog &rarr;</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;
				<a href="/about">About me &rarr;</a>
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
<style>
	main {
		max-width: 720px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2em 1em;
	}
	h1 {
		margin-bottom: 0.15em;
	}
	.tagline {
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-size: 1.1em;
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}
</style>
